est listed as “HH-01” – was listed on sale</a> . The <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-shut-down-kanye-wests-yeezy-website-for-selling-swastika-t-shirt-matthew-koma-responds-with-fuck-ye-merch-3837155">site has since been taken down</a> , and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-x-account-has-been-deactivated-after-bizarre-weekend-rant-3836418">Kanye&#39;s X account has been deactivated</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-protest-video-creator-defends-using-ai-celebs-i-wish-they-would-share-it-3838214">Kanye West protest video creator defends using AI celebs: “I wish they would share it”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
